title: Zoku Fish Pop Mold
description:
For additional information on the featured product please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-1437094/Zoku+Fish+Pop+Mold

 These fanciful pops shaped like undersea denizens are sure to delight children and adults alike. Simply fill the molds with your favorite juice, fruit purée or drink of choice, insert the plastic sticks and freeze. When frozen, pull the pops to release—no need to run under water
